reviewText: This is the best concert even if you don't normally love country music. Waylon Jennings crossed all borders and was the original music Outlaw. A great show; I watch it over and over again.
The best waylon jennings concert ever on DVD, auto great, singing great and great song compilations. Jessica Colter is a bonus
The wrong dvd was placed into my purchased case so I cannot comment on the concert in question but I'm sure it would have been great
